dct_description_sm: "Compiled from air photographs taken by the Royal Air Force 1930 (corrected to March, 1933.)" Map shows Ziārat cantonment boundaries with pillars and numbers; mosques and temples; street names, principal buildings, railways, woods, and tracks. Includes indexes for source compilation, and to sheets used for this map. "Reg. no. 3569 D'34 (F.C. 18-6") 500-X'45." "Copyright reserved."
